proxy

Class TimingProxy

  • java.lang.Object
    • proxy.TimingProxy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.reflect.InvocationHandler

    public class TimingProxy
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.reflect.InvocationHandler
    A proxy class that measures the execution time of methods on a target object. This class implements the InvocationHandler interface and uses Java reflection to invoke methods.
    Since:
    2024-06-15
    See Also:
    InvocationHandler, Method, Proxy
